Dialogue: 1,0:00:59.91,0:01:02.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊  闺蜜帮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.91,0:01:02.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ah, zee Gal Pals
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.37,0:01:05.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村顶级的女子联盟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.37,0:01:05.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bikini Bottom's premier ladies league
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.21,0:01:10.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天  可以看到她们在互相分享绝活
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.21,0:01:07.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Today, we find them
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.00,0:01:10.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,sharing their special skills with one another
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.04,0:01:11.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我一个闺
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.04,0:01:11.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gimme a G
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.30,0:01:12.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我一个蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.30,0:01:12.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gimme an A
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.38,0:01:13.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我一个帮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.38,0:01:13.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gimme an L
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.34,0:01:15.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总共有三个字
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.34,0:01:15.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gimme a P-A-L-S
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.22,0:01:16.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,合起来是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.22,0:01:16.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What does it spell?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.34,0:01:19.22,标准-Chi,,0,1000,0,,闺蜜帮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.34,0:01:19.22,标准-Eng,,0,1000,0,,Gal Pals
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.22,0:01:21.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个啦啦队技巧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.22,0:01:21.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That cheerleading technique
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.39,0:01:25.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能对我们还是太高深了点  珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.39,0:01:25.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,may be a little too advanced for us, Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.48,0:01:30.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后上传鸡蛋  瞧好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.48,0:01:30.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then, upload the eggs, and voila
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.02,0:01:33.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的招牌全息肉糕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:33.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My famous holographic meatloaf
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.16,0:01:41.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.16,0:01:41.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.99,0:01:43.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好不好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.99,0:01:43.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.20,0:01:45.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,非常好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.20,0:01:45.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was delicious
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.62,0:01:46.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.62,0:01:46.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.50,0:01:47.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没什么饱腹感
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.50,0:01:47.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,not too filling
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.37,0:01:52.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,口味还挺清淡的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.37,0:01:52.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It certainly has a light flavor
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.13,0:01:53.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早知道就带零食来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.13,0:01:53.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We should've brought snacks
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.84,0:01:56.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你打算跟大家分享什么呢  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.84,0:01:56.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And what are you sharing with us, Mrs. Puff?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.13,0:02:00.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下面是发动汽船的一个小妙招
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.13,0:02:00.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's an easy way to start your boat
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.09,0:02:02.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以防你碰巧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.09,0:02:02.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just in case you happen to
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.01,0:02:04.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,丢了钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.01,0:02:04.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,lose your keys
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.43,0:02:06.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.43,0:02:06.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I know
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.98,0:02:09.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钥匙被老爸藏起来  还能怎么开船了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:09.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what to do when Daddy hides the boat keys
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.73,0:02:12.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果你们觉得那叫酷的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.73,0:02:12.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If'n y'all thought that was cool
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.48,0:02:14.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等着瞧我秀几招空手道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.48,0:02:14.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,wait till you see my karate demonstration
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.86,0:02:16.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,松鼠功
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.86,0:02:16.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squirrel style
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.82,0:02:22.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的伺服电机可不是造来打架的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.82,0:02:22.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My servos are not built for combat
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.08,0:02:25.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是老师  不是打手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.08,0:02:25.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a teacher, not a fighter
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.54,0:02:27.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我太娇嫩  动不了武
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:27.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm too delicate for martial arts
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.13,0:02:33.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.13,0:02:33.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.50,0:02:36.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这一招可能会让你们改变主意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.50,0:02:36.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This here move might change your mind
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.13,0:02:40.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,停得真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.13,0:02:40.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice parking job
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.55,0:02:41.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.55,0:02:41.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Impressive
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.64,0:02:44.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我太想学空手道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.64,0:02:44.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I totally wanna learn karate
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.56,0:02:46.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,学着我做
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:46.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now do as I do
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.93,0:02:49.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且别忘了全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.93,0:02:49.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and remember, give it all your gumption
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.94,0:02:51.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,松鼠功
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.94,0:02:51.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squirrel style
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.98,0:02:56.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,松鼠功
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.98,0:02:56.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squirrel style
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.11,0:03:00.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,几小时后
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.74,0:03:08.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这空手道课上得可真是带劲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.74,0:03:08.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was one humdinger of a karate lesson
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.87,0:03:12.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我等不及要上下一节课了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.87,0:03:12.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't wait until our next one
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.63,0:03:14.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恐怕已经没什么可教的了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.63,0:03:14.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'Fraid there ain't much more I can teach you
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.96,0:03:17.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说实话  你们学得太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.96,0:03:17.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In fact, y'all are such great students
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.71,0:03:20.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我要给你们颁发终极橡子腰带
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.71,0:03:20.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm awardin' you my ultimate acorn belt
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.22,0:03:24.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,毛茸茸的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:24.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So fuzzy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.51,0:03:25.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.51,0:03:25.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.76,0:03:28.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我  我可能需要个小点的尺寸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.76,0:03:28.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I-I may need a smaller size
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.14,0:03:31.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,松鼠功
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.14,0:03:31.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squirrel Style
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.98,0:03:35.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下周见  闺蜜帮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.98,0:03:35.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you next week, Gal Pals
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.61,0:03:37.44,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(966,798)}闺蜜帮
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.48,0:03:39.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.48,0:03:39.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Daddy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.86,0:03:41.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:41.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm home
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.40,0:03:44.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在楼上  乖女儿珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.40,0:03:44.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm up here, Pearly girl
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.49,0:03:48.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可算是来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.49,0:03:48.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, it's about time
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.29,0:03:49.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你没洗的臭衣服都堆成山了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.29,0:03:49.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your stinky laundry's piling up
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.83,0:03:50.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老爸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.83,0:03:50.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Daddy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.83,0:03:52.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才没有那么臭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.83,0:03:52.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not that bad
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.13,0:04:00.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真没那么臭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.13,0:04:00.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not that bad, eh?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.55,0:04:01.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好好好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:01.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fine
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.47,0:04:05.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,臭烘烘的破衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.47,0:04:05.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stupid stinky clothes
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.85,0:04:07.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,松鼠功
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:07.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squirrel style
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.39,0:04:13.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这一劈  很清新
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.39,0:04:13.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Karate fresh
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.20,0:04:26.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有什么是空手道做不到的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:26.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is there anything karate can't do?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.28,0:04:31.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快啊  你这破铜烂铁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.28,0:04:31.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, you pile of flotsam
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.29,0:04:33.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我下节上课就要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.29,0:04:33.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll be late for my next lesson
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.63,0:04:38.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比接线点火还简单
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.63,0:04:38.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Even easier than hot-wiring it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.13,0:04:39.96,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(572,810)}海之霸
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.13,0:04:43.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老婆好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.13,0:04:43.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, hon
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.80,0:04:45.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只是在把我的变异
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:45.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just putting my mutant
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.64,0:04:46.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海霸糊怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.64,0:04:46.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,chum monster
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.35,0:04:48.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,捉回笼子里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.35,0:04:48.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,back in its cage
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.85,0:04:51.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  大力士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.85,0:04:51.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure, Hercules
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.52,0:04:53.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来帮你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:53.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me give you a hand
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.02,0:04:59.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.02,0:04:59.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not ba--
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.32,0:05:01.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,松鼠功
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.32,0:05:01.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squirrel style
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.87,0:05:11.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是珊迪  有求必应
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.87,0:05:11.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Y'all reached Sandy, the squirrel that's handy
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.58,0:05:13.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  我是痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:13.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy, it's Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.12,0:05:14.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快来帮帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.12,0:05:14.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You have to help me
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.17,0:05:22.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出了什么麻烦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:22.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What seems to be the trouble?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.59,0:05:24.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凯伦失控了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.59,0:05:24.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Karen's outta control
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.38,0:05:26.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不管你之前对她干嘛了  赶紧撤销掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.38,0:05:26.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Undo whatever you did to her
Dialogue: 1,0:05:26.93,0:05:28.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干嘛怪我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:28.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, what are you blamin' me for?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.72,0:05:31.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,松鼠功
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.72,0:05:31.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squirrel style
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.77,0:05:33.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.77,0:05:33.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Point taken
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.23,0:05:37.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  凯伦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.23,0:05:37.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How-do, Karen?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.40,0:05:38.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在干嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.40,0:05:38.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What you up to?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.90,0:05:39.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.90,0:05:39.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.94,0:05:42.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在忙着重新装修实验室
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.94,0:05:42.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I'm a little busy redecorating the lab
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.86,0:05:45.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拆毁还差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:45.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,More like demolishing
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.70,0:05:49.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下门口有风水了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.70,0:05:49.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now the doorway is feng shui
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.95,0:05:54.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这空手道打得可能有点过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:54.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You may have gone a little overboard on the karate
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.75,0:05:56.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这明明就是你说的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.75,0:05:56.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's like you said
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.33,0:05:58.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.33,0:05:58.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give it all your gumption
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.21,0:05:59.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,松鼠功
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:05:59.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squirrel style
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.05,0:06:05.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好像还真那么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.05,0:06:05.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I did say that, didn't I?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.97,0:06:10.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这地方一直缺个窗户
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.97,0:06:10.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This place always needed a window
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.68,0:06:12.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,松鼠功
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.68,0:06:12.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squirrel style
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.47,0:06:13.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.47,0:06:13.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh no
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.68,0:06:14.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我等会儿回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.68,0:06:14.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Be back later
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.60,0:06:16.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.60,0:06:16.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.52,0:06:19.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎随时过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.52,0:06:19.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Drop by anytime
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.86,0:06:25.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快逃命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.86,0:06:25.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Run for your life
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.86,0:06:27.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,保命要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:27.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Save yourselves
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.45,0:06:30.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,毁大号简直惨无人道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.45,0:06:30.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The tuba-manity
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.32,0:06:35.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一个空一个手一个道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:35.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gimme a K-A-R-A-T-E
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.08,0:06:36.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,合起来是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.08,0:06:36.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's it spell?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.54,0:06:38.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,空手道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:38.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Karate
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.04,0:06:42.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.04,0:06:42.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.63,0:06:46.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍  我感觉啦啦队跟空手道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.63,0:06:46.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pearl, I'm not sure cheerleading and karate
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.38,0:06:47.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好像不太搭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.38,0:06:47.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,are a great mix
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.97,0:06:49.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.97,0:06:49.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.05,0:06:50.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多亏了空手道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.05,0:06:50.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks to karate
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.18,0:06:52.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在是全校最棒的啦啦队员了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.18,0:06:52.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am the best cheerleader in school
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.01,0:06:54.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.01,0:06:54.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's true
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.60,0:06:56.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她可神了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.60,0:06:56.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She's amazing
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.10,0:06:58.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我还是觉得不太
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:06:58.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I still don't think--
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.06,0:07:00.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,松鼠功
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.06,0:07:00.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squirrel style
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.14,0:07:00.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.14,0:07:00.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh no
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.19,0:07:03.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是请你少打点空手道好吗  珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.19,0:07:03.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Try to tone down the karate, will ya, Pearl?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.73,0:07:05.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,松鼠功
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.73,0:07:05.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squirrel style
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:06.23,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(674,908)}好
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.07,0:07:11.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,松鼠功
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.07,0:07:11.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squirrel style
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.24,0:07:15.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡芙到底在搞什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:15.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What in tarnation is Puff doin'?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.41,0:07:20.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.41,0:07:20.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Howdy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.58,0:07:22.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在干嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:22.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whatcha doin'?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.42,0:07:23.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:23.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.29,0:07:27.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我把你那个厉害的空手道技巧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.29,0:07:27.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've integrated your wonderful karate skills
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.09,0:07:29.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,融入到我的驾驶课里了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.09,0:07:29.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,into my driver's training
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.38,0:07:32.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终于能好好给海绵宝宝上课了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.38,0:07:32.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can finally give SpongeBob lessons
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.05,0:07:34.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会再伤害到别人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.05,0:07:34.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,without anyone getting hurt
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.64,0:07:37.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别忘了打转向灯  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:37.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't forget your turn signal, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.35,0:07:41.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你那个新的教学方式
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.35,0:07:41.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your new teaching method is
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.65,0:07:43.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别开上人行道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.65,0:07:43.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get off the sidewalk
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.69,0:07:46.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太有效率了  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.69,0:07:46.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,certainly effective, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.07,0:07:49.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我觉得你终于准备好了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.07,0:07:49.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think you're finally ready, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.53,0:07:50.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,踩油门
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.53,0:07:50.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Floor it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.70,0:07:51.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,踩油门吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.70,0:07:51.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Floor it?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.61,0:07:52.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.61,0:07:52.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You heard me
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.99,0:07:54.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,油门踩到底
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.99,0:07:54.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pedal to the metal
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.16,0:07:59.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,松鼠功
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.16,0:07:59.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squirrel Style
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.33,0:08:02.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.33,0:08:02.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh no
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.62,0:08:06.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我创造了三个空手道怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.62,0:08:06.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've created three karate monsters
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.01,0:08:11.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,松鼠功
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.01,0:08:11.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squirrel style
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.80,0:08:17.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.80,0:08:17.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.97,0:08:20.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然今晚得练空手道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.97,0:08:20.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know we're supposed to practice karate tonight
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.60,0:08:24.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可这驾驶课上得简直累死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:24.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but my driving lesson really took a lot out of me
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.57,0:08:28.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.57,0:08:28.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gosh, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.98,0:08:29.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.98,0:08:29.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.98,0:08:32.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自从我给闺蜜帮上了空手道课
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.98,0:08:32.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ever since I gave the Gal Pals karate lessons
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.78,0:08:35.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她们个个都成了跆拳呆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:35.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,they've all gone tae kwon dodo
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.87,0:08:39.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果说问题是教会她们空手道引起的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.87,0:08:39.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, if teaching them karate caused the problem
Dialogue: 1,0:08:40.20,0:08:42.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就反过来  把教的都收回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.20,0:08:42.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,why don't you just un-teach it?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.58,0:08:44.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那简直是最傻的一个建议
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:44.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that would be the dumbest suggestion ever
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.42,0:08:49.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好在我早就发明了个反向空手道矩阵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.42,0:08:49.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if'n I hadn't already invented a reverse karate matrix
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.00,0:08:50.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完全可以实现你的建议
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:50.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that does exactly that
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.55,0:08:53.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第一步  瞄准泡芙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.55,0:08:53.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Step one: Zero in on Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.51,0:08:55.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍  和凯伦的大脑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.51,0:08:55.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pearl, and Karen's brains
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.76,0:08:58.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能帮忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.76,0:08:58.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I help?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.72,0:08:59.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.72,0:08:59.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, sure
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.85,0:09:01.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就只要转动那个旋钮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.85,0:09:01.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All you gotta do is twist that dial
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.77,0:09:03.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拉动这根拉杆  往上扳那开关
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.77,0:09:03.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,pull this here lever, flip those switches
Dialogue: 1,0:09:03.60,0:09:05.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,压那踏板  再按下这小按钮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.60,0:09:05.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,press that pedal, and push this little button
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.19,0:09:06.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,做一百次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.19,0:09:06.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do that a hundred times
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.48,0:09:07.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,按刚刚的顺序来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.48,0:09:07.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In that order
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.44,0:09:09.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:09.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.69,0:09:11.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.69,0:09:11.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ready?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.07,0:09:14.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在我只要反向使出空手道招数就行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.07,0:09:12.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now all I have to do
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.28,0:09:14.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is perform all my karate moves in reverse
Dialogue: 1,0:09:15.20,0:09:16.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,按那颗按钮  压那个踏板
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:16.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Push that button, press that pedal
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.95,0:09:18.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,按那根拉杆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.95,0:09:18.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,push that lever
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.20,0:09:19.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,转那个旋钮吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.20,0:09:19.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Twist that dial?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.43,0:09:46.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,第二天早上
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.06,0:09:50.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样应该就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.06,0:09:50.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That oughta do it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.11,0:09:52.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.11,0:09:52.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whoopee
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.90,0:09:59.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,闺蜜帮的空手道危害不到裤头村了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:09:59.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bikini Bottom is safe from the Gal Pals' karate chaos
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.82,0:10:01.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,松鼠功
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.82,0:10:01.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squirrel style
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.49,0:10:02.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,并非如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.49,0:10:02.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe not
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.79,0:10:05.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要把脚邮寄到你面前  布兰奇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.79,0:10:05.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna deliver my foot to your face, Blanche
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.96,0:10:08.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好大的胆子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.96,0:10:08.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How dare you
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.63,0:10:18.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这空手道很适合用来健身
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.63,0:10:18.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This karate stuff is a great workout
Dialogue: 1,0:10:19.14,0:10:23.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你打不过我的末日转轮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.14,0:10:23.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You are no match for my spinning wheels of doom
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.01,0:10:24.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看我大力使出
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.01,0:10:24.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Behold the power of
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.72,0:10:25.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的腿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.72,0:10:25.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my leg
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.18,0:10:31.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你当时扳开关跟按按钮的顺序没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.18,0:10:28.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You did make sure to flip all the switches
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.35,0:10:31.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and push the buttons in the correct order, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.02,0:10:35.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好像我该往上扳的时候往下扳了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:35.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I may have flicked when I should've flipped
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.24,0:10:37.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真见鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.24,0:10:37.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dang-gummit
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.19,0:10:39.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没让闺蜜帮忘掉空手道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.19,0:10:39.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Instead of de-karateing the Gal Pals
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.66,0:10:43.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反倒让裤头村所有人成了空手道大师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.66,0:10:43.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I done turned everyone in town into a karate master
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.29,0:10:47.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,空手道太神了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.29,0:10:47.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ka-ra-te is ah-mazing
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.83,0:10:50.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,助步器旋风劈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.83,0:10:50.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spinning walker whirlwind
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.92,0:10:53.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.92,0:10:53.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now what do we do?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.92,0:10:56.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道  不过大伙儿玩得还挺开心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.92,0:10:56.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No idea, but they're sure having fun
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.81,0:11:10.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然大家都摸透了彼此之间的招数
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.81,0:11:10.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess since everyone knows each other's karate moves
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.27,0:11:12.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就没人能分得出输赢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:12.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,no one is winning or losing
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.23,0:11:13.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然没人受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.23,0:11:13.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And if no one's getting hurt
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.98,0:11:15.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就没有问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.98,0:11:15.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's no problem
Dialogue: 1,0:11:15.90,0:11:19.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那么打不过就加入吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:19.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, if'n you can't beat 'em, join 'em
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.99,0:11:21.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.99,0:11:21.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shall we?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.41,0:11:23.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你先请  师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.41,0:11:23.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,After you, sensei
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.57,0:11:25.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,松鼠功
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.57,0:11:25.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squirrel style
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.95,0:11:29.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,于是  多亏了闺蜜帮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.95,0:11:29.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And so, thanks to zee Gal Pals
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.50,0:11:32.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们得向裤头村珍重告别
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.50,0:11:32.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we must bid adieu to Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.17,0:11:35.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打招呼迎接  空手道村
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:35.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and say bonjour to Karate Bottom
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.08,0:11:36.17,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(884,256)}空手道村
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.17,0:11:40.76,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\fsp40\c&H00FFC1&}凯伦的茶话会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.97,0:11:42.13,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(752,430)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.97,0:11:42.13,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(770,722)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.97,0:11:46.60,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1530,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:43.59,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(636,484)}指导总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:43.59,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(800,700)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.89,0:11:45.05,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(740,548)}统筹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.35,0:11:46.51,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(596,560)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.81,0:11:48.22,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(640,598)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.81,0:11:48.22,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1468.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.31,0:11:53.52,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(672,758)}海之霸
Dialogue: 1,0:11:50.56,0:11:52.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上好餐巾被我放哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.56,0:11:52.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where did I put the good napkins?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.07,0:11:57.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.07,0:11:57.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's better
Dialogue: 1,0:11:57.07,0:11:59.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样是不是很好看啊  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.07,0:11:59.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Doesn't this look nice, Plankton?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.20,0:12:01.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.20,0:12:01.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.87,0:12:08.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凯伦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.87,0:12:08.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Karen
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.91,0:12:10.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帮我续杯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.91,0:12:10.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Need a refill
Dialogue: 1,0:12:10.54,0:12:12.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,顺便再帮我打点薯片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.54,0:12:12.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And some more chips while you're at it
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.00,0:12:13.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:13.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.92,0:12:18.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都跟你说了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.92,0:12:18.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I told you
Dialogue: 1,0:12:18.09,0:12:21.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有几位电脑朋友今天要来共进午餐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.09,0:12:21.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my computer friends are coming over today for lunch
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.84,0:12:25.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上给我把这堆破烂搬你实验室去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.84,0:12:25.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You need to move all of this into your lab right now
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.18,0:12:29.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还共进午餐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.18,0:12:29.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's still happening?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.97,0:12:32.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可惜我还要追剧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.97,0:12:32.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Too bad, I'm watching my stories
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.86,0:12:41.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要追剧就在这里面追
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.86,0:12:41.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can watch your "stories" in here
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.32,0:12:48.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实  你最好一直待在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.32,0:12:48.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In fact, it might be best if you stayed in here
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.58,0:12:49.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等我朋友走了再出来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.58,0:12:49.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,until my friends leave
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.79,0:12:50.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.79,0:12:50.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.83,0:12:52.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不准把我晾在一边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.83,0:12:52.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't put me on ice
Dialogue: 1,0:12:53.21,0:12:55.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是嫌我丢人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.21,0:12:55.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you ashamed of me?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.84,0:13:00.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然不是了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:13:00.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course not
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.13,0:13:02.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.13,0:13:02.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're here
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.05,0:13:03.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我待在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:03.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stay in here for me
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.51,0:13:08.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该能拦住他了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.51,0:13:08.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That oughta hold him
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.27,0:13:13.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,电脑茶话会的小伙伴们好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.27,0:13:13.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, computer klatch
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.18,0:13:15.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临海之霸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.18,0:13:15.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Chum Bucket
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.35,0:13:16.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.35,0:13:16.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.02,0:13:16.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.02,0:13:16.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Greetings
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.57,0:13:24.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:24.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.70,0:13:34.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一群鬼东西哔哔个不停
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:34.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bunch of babbling beepers
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.17,0:13:38.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反正我还得干活呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.17,0:13:38.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got work to do anyway
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.75,0:13:44.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好久不见了  凯伦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.75,0:13:44.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's been way too long, Karen
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.01,0:13:46.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也很高兴再见到你  坦迪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:46.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great to see you too, Tandy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.47,0:13:48.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自从我们上次寒暄几句以来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.47,0:13:48.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Since we last exchanged pleasantries
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.34,0:13:54.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我编码了7486099个二进制文件
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.34,0:13:54.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have encoded 7,486,099 new files of binary code
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.10,0:13:58.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,00011111111000000000
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:58.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,00011111111000000000--
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.77,0:14:03.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,音量调低一点  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.77,0:14:03.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dial it down, dude
Dialogue: 1,0:14:04.32,0:14:07.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你近来如何  比姆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.32,0:14:07.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And how are things with you, BIM?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.57,0:14:11.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不要来抱一个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.57,0:14:11.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"How about a hug?"
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.53,0:14:13.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.53,0:14:13.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come here
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.91,0:14:19.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别这么用力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.91,0:14:19.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Not so hard"?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.17,0:14:20.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  比姆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.17,0:14:20.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, BIM
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.54,0:14:23.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开个玩笑嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.54,0:14:23.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Just kidding
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.88,0:14:27.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我又没有知觉什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.88,0:14:27.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have no feelings of sensation whatsoever"
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.89,0:14:32.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啥玩意突然就那么好笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.89,0:14:32.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's so funny all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.35,0:14:36.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看他们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:36.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at 'em
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.60,0:14:38.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多半在议论我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.60,0:14:38.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I bet they're talking about me
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.14,0:14:40.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还在嘲笑我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.14,0:14:40.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're laughing at me
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.40,0:14:46.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要知道他们在哔哔我什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.40,0:14:46.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I gotta know what they're beeping and bleeping about me
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.94,0:14:48.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:48.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know what to do
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.04,0:15:03.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.04,0:15:03.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.59,0:15:06.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我应该得去上个洗手间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.59,0:15:06.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess I have to use the little calculator's room
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.26,0:15:09.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比姆  当时是你说了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.26,0:15:09.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,BIM, you were the one who said--
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.26,0:15:14.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早知道出门之前就上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.26,0:15:14.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I should have done this before I left the house
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.68,0:15:15.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,执行下载程序
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.68,0:15:15.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Commence download
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.09,0:15:51.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终于啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.09,0:15:51.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Finally
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.09,0:15:52.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坦迪回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.09,0:15:52.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tandy's back
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.43,0:15:52.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咋了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.43,0:15:52.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.97,0:15:54.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是掉马桶里了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:54.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you fall in?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.68,0:16:01.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实  猜猜我还撞见谁了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.68,0:16:01.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes I did fall in, and guess who I ran into?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.14,0:16:03.69,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1024,920)}母
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.14,0:16:03.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们的主板
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.14,0:16:03.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your motherboard
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.40,0:16:07.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太过分了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.40,0:16:07.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Too much?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.61,0:16:10.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.61,0:16:10.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.24,0:16:12.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真好笑  坦迪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.24,0:16:12.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good one, Tandy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.07,0:16:15.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她信了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.07,0:16:15.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She bought it
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.41,0:16:16.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.41,0:16:16.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.62,0:16:19.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我错过了什么有料的坏话没
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:19.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what juicy trash talk did I miss?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.16,0:16:20.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有料的坏话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:20.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Juicy trash talk?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:20.54,0:16:23.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是指恶意软件故障吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.54,0:16:23.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You mean a "malware glitch"?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.42,0:16:24.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.42,0:16:24.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.17,0:16:25.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,文件损坏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.17,0:16:25.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Corrupt files"?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.50,0:16:26.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.50,0:16:26.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.88,0:16:30.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.88,0:16:30.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.26,0:16:31.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才不是黑客
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.26,0:16:31.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not "Hackers"
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.42,0:16:32.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我指的是八卦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.42,0:16:32.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean gossip
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.93,0:16:35.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,家丑  传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.93,0:16:35.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dirty laundry, rumors
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.09,0:16:36.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谣言  闲话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.09,0:16:36.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,canards, tittle-tattles
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.97,0:16:38.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快快爆料
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.97,0:16:38.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spill the tea
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.56,0:16:40.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁的八卦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:40.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,About who?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.02,0:16:42.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道  比如说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.02,0:16:42.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know, like, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.56,0:16:44.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凯伦的丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.56,0:16:44.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Karen's husband?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.02,0:16:46.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是说  那个绿色的小怪东西咋回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.02,0:16:46.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, what is the deal with that little green weirdo?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.52,0:16:47.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说得对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:47.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.94,0:16:51.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,配餐的来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.94,0:16:51.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The caterer is here
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.78,0:16:52.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有配餐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.78,0:16:52.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Catering?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:52.61,0:16:53.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好高级
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.61,0:16:53.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fancy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.53,0:16:56.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来他们并没有议论我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.53,0:16:56.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess they're not talking about me after all
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.70,0:16:58.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凭什么不议论我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.70,0:16:58.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why aren't they talking about me?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.66,0:17:01.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,电脑茶话会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.66,0:17:01.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Computer klatch
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.87,0:17:03.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是你们的服务生  海绵机
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:03.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am your server, SpongeBot
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.96,0:17:06.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,邀请你们来大吃特吃这一GB
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.96,0:17:06.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I invite you to take a giga-bite
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.83,0:17:10.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王的美食
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.83,0:17:10.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of the Krusty Krab's delectable comestibles
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.09,0:17:14.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.09,0:17:14.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Krusty Krab?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.09,0:17:20.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有蜂蜜辣芥末螺帽螺栓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.09,0:17:20.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've got spicy honey-mustard nuts and bolts
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.47,0:17:21.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,奶酪软盘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.47,0:17:21.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,cheesy floppy discs
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.93,0:17:24.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以及电脑芯片  配散热硅脂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.93,0:17:24.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and computer chips with thermal grease
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.15,0:17:28.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吃好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:28.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yum, yum, yum
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.15,0:17:29.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,电脑食物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.15,0:17:29.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Computer food?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.82,0:17:30.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.82,0:17:30.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lame
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.48,0:17:33.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还要用勺子给大家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.48,0:17:33.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I will spoon feed you all
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.57,0:17:36.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都来喂一口这道辣菜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.57,0:17:36.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a sample of this spicy concoction
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.00,0:17:45.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这口给你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:45.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And one for you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.87,0:17:46.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我自己就能吃这
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.87,0:17:46.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can feed my--
Dialogue: 1,0:17:50.63,0:17:52.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以失陪一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.63,0:17:52.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would you excuse me for a moment?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.34,0:17:57.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道坦迪为什么老是往洗手间跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.34,0:17:57.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wonder why Tandy keeps going to the restroom
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.47,0:17:58.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该检查一下他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.47,0:17:58.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I should check on him
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.51,0:18:03.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.51,0:18:03.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh no
Dialogue: 1,0:18:03.56,0:18:06.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得检查他的生命体征  看有没有病毒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.56,0:18:06.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll check his vital signs for a virus
Dialogue: 1,0:18:08.69,0:18:10.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来这病毒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.69,0:18:10.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like this "virus"
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.65,0:18:14.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不愿意老实听话  乖乖待在实验室里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.65,0:18:14.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,couldn't just stay in his lab like I asked
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.24,0:18:18.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你没事吧  坦迪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.24,0:18:18.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everything okay in here, Tandy?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.57,0:18:20.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一点赛博网络病罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.57,0:18:20.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just a little cyber-sickness
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.74,0:18:22.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总之这次拜访很美好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.74,0:18:22.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I've had a lovely visit
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.49,0:18:24.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我觉得自己应该要回家断电了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.49,0:18:24.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I think I should go home and power down
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.87,0:18:27.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可别这就开溜啊  坦迪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.87,0:18:27.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't bail on us now, Tandy
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.21,0:18:30.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派对才刚要开始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.21,0:18:30.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The party is just getting started
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.08,0:18:34.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来玩个电脑室内游戏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.08,0:18:34.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's play a computer parlor game
Dialogue: 1,0:18:36.42,0:18:39.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了  来玩电火花手指吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.42,0:18:39.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know, let's play Sparky Finger
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.11,0:18:57.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不来玩一玩电脑叠罗汉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.11,0:18:57.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or how about Compu-Tower
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.70,0:19:03.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到你了  坦迪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.70,0:19:03.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your turn, Tandy
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.61,0:19:36.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好主意  比姆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.61,0:19:36.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great idea, BIM
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.86,0:19:39.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁想玩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.86,0:19:39.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who wants to play
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.86,0:19:42.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拳打粉碎机器人大战
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:42.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Punch 'Em Crunch 'Em Robots"
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.08,0:19:45.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拳打吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.08,0:19:45.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Punch 'em?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.83,0:19:46.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,粉碎吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.83,0:19:46.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Crunch 'em?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.21,0:19:56.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家装好数字拳头  准备好打得
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.21,0:19:56.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Put up your digital dukes and get ready to have your
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.38,0:19:59.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,脑袋开花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:19:59.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Noggin knocked off
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.34,0:20:04.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,笨死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.34,0:20:04.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The stupidity
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.85,0:20:07.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,戴上手套  坦迪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.85,0:20:07.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Put your gloves on, Tandy
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.43,0:20:10.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在这个时候应该适合我来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.43,0:20:10.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This would probably be a good time for me to, uh
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.19,0:20:14.77,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1468,178)}出口
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.06,0:20:13.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.06,0:20:13.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.44,0:20:20.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第一回合
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.44,0:20:20.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Round one
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.79,0:20:38.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第二回合
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.79,0:20:38.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Round two
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.93,0:20:54.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这电脑茶话会好疯狂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.93,0:20:54.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These computer klatch parties are insane
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.69,0:21:00.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第三回合
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.69,0:21:00.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Round three
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.11,0:21:02.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.11,0:21:02.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not again
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.75,0:21:14.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来个左勾拳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.75,0:21:14.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give 'em a left
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.71,0:21:15.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,右勾拳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.71,0:21:15.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And a right
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.58,0:21:17.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再一记正中下巴的上勾拳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.58,0:21:17.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And a line drive right up the middle
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.26,0:21:26.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干嘛不玩算数字账的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.26,0:21:26.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't we play a game that crunches numbers
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.84,0:21:28.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别打我脑袋  算我的账
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.84,0:21:28.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,instead of heads?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.05,0:21:29.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道你就在里面  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.05,0:21:29.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know you're in there, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.85,0:21:32.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且我要把你打得脑袋开花
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.85,0:21:32.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I'm knockin' your noggin off
Dialogue: 1,0:21:44.86,0:21:46.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那不是坦迪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.86,0:21:46.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not Tandy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.66,0:21:50.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢尔顿  你干什么偷窥我们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.66,0:21:50.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Alright, Sheldon, why were you spying on us?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.62,0:21:54.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我以为你跟你朋友都嫌弃我  抹黑我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.62,0:21:54.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I thought you and your friends were hating on me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.38,0:22:00.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这小不点是在被害妄想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.38,0:22:00.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You paranoid pipsqueak
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.00,0:22:03.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们才不讨厌你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.00,0:22:03.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We don't hate you
Dialogue: 1,0:22:04.13,0:22:06.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以说你们没对我生气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.13,0:22:06.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You-you mean you're not mad at me?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.63,0:22:07.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.63,0:22:07.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.80,0:22:10.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过有个人肯定很生气
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.80,0:22:10.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I know someone who is
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.39,0:22:13.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把我身体还回来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.39,0:22:13.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me back my body
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.15,0:22:22.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.15,0:22:22.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.90,0:22:23.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.90,0:22:23.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.86,0:22:25.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.86,0:22:25.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.07,0:22:27.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.07,0:22:27.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Beep
